              <div style="width: 64px; height: 64px; border-radius: 16px; background: rgba(74,222,128,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(74,222,128,0.15); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 8px;">
                <span style="font-size: 28px;">📦</span>
