            </div>
            <div style="background: #08080f; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 14px; margin-top: 1rem; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.8; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">
